settings.custom_liquid:
{% comment %}
  Template: Refund Policy
  This page outlines our refund policy for products purchased from Trezon.
{% endcomment %}

<div class="refund-policy-container">
  <h1>Refund Policy</h1>

  <section class="refund-section">
    <h2>1. Eligibility for Refund</h2>
    <p>We offer a refund on items purchased from Trezon if they meet the following criteria:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>The item is unused, undamaged, and in the original packaging.</li>
      <li>The refund request is made within 14 days of receiving the product.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="refund-section">
    <h2>2. How to Request a Refund</h2>
    <p>To request a refund, please follow these steps:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Contact our customer service team at <a href="mailto:trezon.in@gmail.com">trezon.in@gmail.com</a> within 14 days of receiving your product.</li>
      <li>Provide your order number, a brief description of the reason for the refund, and pictures of the product (if applicable).</li>
      <li>Our team will review your request and issue the refund if eligible.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="refund-section">
    <h2>3. Non-Refundable Items</h2>
    <p>Some items are not eligible for a refund, including:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Products that have been used or damaged after delivery.</li>
      <li>Personalized or custom-made products.</li>
      <li>Items purchased during a promotional sale or clearance sale.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="refund-section">
    <h2>4. Refund Process</h2>
    <p>Once your refund request is approved, the process will typically take 7-10 business days. The refund will be credited back to the original payment method.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="refund-section">
    <h2>5. Shipping Costs</h2>
    <p>Please note that the original shipping costs are non-refundable. If you are eligible for a refund, you will be reimbursed for the product cost only. Return shipping fees may apply and are the responsibility of the customer unless the item was defective or incorrect.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="refund-section">
    <h2>6. Need Help?</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance with your refund request, feel free to contact our customer support team at <a href="mailto:trezon.in@gmail.com">trezon.in@gmail.com</a></p>
  </section>
</div>

<style>
  .refund-policy-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 20px;
    background: #EEDFA4; /* Background color */
    border-radius: 10px;
  }
  .refund-section {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .refund-section h2 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .refund-section p, .refund-section ul {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #333;
  }
  .refund-section ul {
    list-style-type: disc;
    margin-left: 20px;
  }
  .refund-section a {
    color: #392D00;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .refund-section a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
